      "span_text": "The similar conclusions from the cell cycle data has been proven by previous study.  The combination of UA and irradiation could also cause more apoptotic cell death as shown by Fig 3B. The proportion of apoptotic cells substantially increased by application of both UA and irradiation in BGC-823 cells as opposed to UA or IR treatment alone (78.2% VS 9.6% and 12.5%, p<0.01, Fig 3D) ."
